cal numerical simulations.\nAdditionally, grains are heated by CRs to modest temperatures (20--30 K) with\nintervals of a few years, which reduces the possibility of ice chemical\nexplosions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 May 2016 07:11:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-06"}
