 the principal\nvascular trees. The simulated tissue density corresponding to the CT\nexamination output reflects a pathology modeled as a localized permeability\ndeficiency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 May 2016 10:12:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-01"}
