ding site, and the second one allows to\nenforce the desired secondary structure on the peptide structure. Based on the\ngiven example, we observe significant improvement of the docking accuracy in\ncomparison to the default CABS-dock mode.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 May 2016 15:17:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-31"}
