provide insights on key success\nfactors for the effective adoption and institutionalization of enterprise\ngamification initiatives in organizations, and subsequently help them enhance\nthe performance of their employees and drive positive business outcomes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 29 May 2016 20:41:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-01"}
